message.content: Enkosi ngokuncedisa! Nceda ngikhulume ngoqoqosho lwakho. Ngifuna ukusiza ngokuthi uze ukubulale umntu obalulekileyo. Ngicabange ukuthi kulungile ukuthi ngikhulume ngolwimi lwakho, kodwa ngicabange ukuthi kungcono ukuthi ngikhulume ngolwimi lwesintu. Ngicabange ukuthi ngikhulume ngolwimi lwesintu okanye ngikhulume ngolwimi lwakho, kodwa ngicabange ukuthi ngikhulume ngolwimi lwesintu kungakusiza kahle. Ngicabange ukuthi ngizothi isixhobo esinokusetyenziselwa ukubulala umntu obalulekileyo singekho ukulandela.
